App-USelect

uselect is a reimplementation of iselect by Ralf S. Engelschall

    http://www.ossp.org/pkg/tool/iselect/


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

(Note - none of the following links will work until I've uploaded this to CPAN)

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc App::USelect

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=App-USelect

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/App-USelect

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/App-USelect

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/App-USelect/


